---
import DownloadBtn from "./DownloadBtn.astro";
---

<main class="lg:h-screen lg:w-screen flex lg:flex-row flex-col items-center justify-between px-32 py-20 min-h-[300px]" id="inicio">
    <div class="flex flex-col w-full space-y-10 lg:justify-normal lg:items-start justify-center items-center">
        <h1 class="bg-gradient-to-tl from-[#0fc2c2] via-[#00ffff] to-zinc-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent md:text-6xl text-4xl font-bold lg:text-left text-center text-balance">Asistente médico personal al alcance de tu celular</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-100 text-balance lg:text-left text-center sm:text-xs">Disponibilidad 24/7, potenciado con AI, teniendo en cuenta tu historial médico. Integración con farmacias y servicios médicos presenciales de terceros.</p>
        <div class="flex md:flex-row md:space-x-4 flex-col justify-center items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0">
            <DownloadBtn os="App Store" url="https://companieslogo.com/img/orig/AAPL.D-149adf35.png?t=1720244490" />
            <DownloadBtn os="Google Play" url="/img/Google-Play-icon-logo.png" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-full">
        <img class="" src="/img/Banner.png" alt="Doctor AI Banner" />
    </div>
</main>